    email: bcraytor@proton.me
    orcid: "https://orcid.org/0000-0003-2219-9156"
date-released: "2026-03-22"
abstract: >-
  Provides a Shiny-based graphical user interface for the earth package,
  enabling interactive building and exploration of Multivariate Adaptive
  Regression Splines (MARS) models. Features include data import from CSV
  and Excel files, automatic detection of categorical variables, interactive
  control of interaction terms via an allowed matrix, comprehensive model
  diagnostics with variable importance and partial dependence plots, and
  publication-quality report generation via Quarto.
